  "original_title": "Police curfew is not recognized: Sumanthiran",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Police curfew is not recognized: Sumanthiran",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Parliamentarian M.A. Sumanthiran says that there is no legal framework for the Police to impose curfew.",
        "Issuing a statement, the MP stated that there is no express legal provision which statutorily empowers the Police to impose",
        "curfew, and added that this is an unlawful announcement to discourage people to gather tomorrow to protest against the Government.",
        "The Government took steps to impose Police curfew to several areas in the Western Province earlier, including Negombo Division, Kelaniya Division, Nugegoda Division, Mount Lavinia Division, Colombo (North) Division, Colombo (South) Division and the Colombo (Central) Division.",
        "Govt should Not Try and Curtail The People\u2019s Right of Expression \u2013 Sajith",
        "#Rambukkana Shooting: Human Rights Commission makes startling revelations in report"
      ],
